cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with physical layer security in wireless communication systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of feedback in the multiple access wiretap channel is also a topic related to networked systems (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). Finally, the Gaussian example mentioned in the paper suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
